
***** SetColor: set the same color all vertices of a surface *******

token(s):
T_SetColor	SetColor

rule(s):
commande <-- VAR_SURFACE '.' T_SetColor '(' expr ',' expr ',' expr ')'


parameters
  # VAR_SURFACE: input surface
  # expr: red   (0-255)
  # expr: green (0-255)
  # expr: blue  (0-255)

description:
Set the same color all vertices of a surface.


See Also:
	ColorMaterial


